<P>
   BAYLOR-RHODEN-COLUMN (New York) _ Chicago Cubs manager Don
Baylor arrives at Shea Stadium for a three-game series with the
Mets, and the questions everyone has for him concern his ongoing
feud with Bobby Valentine. But against that backdrop, Baylor also
has something to say about Patrick Ewing, who, like Baylor, has
spent much of his professional playing career in quest of a
championship ring. Baylor finally got his ring _ at the age of 38.
