</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-INTERNET-THIRDWORLD-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WHEN VILLAGES GO GLOBAL: HOW A BYTE OF KNOWLEDGE CAN BE DANGEROUS,
TOO 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
