<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-22 11:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4232 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-DOWD-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      04-22 0726
