   BBO-MINORS-NEWPARK _ CHATTANOOGA, Tenn. _ After 70 years at
Engle Stadium, baseball has a new home in Chattanooga. BellSouth
Ballpark is one of the few privately financed stadiums in the
minors. Owner Frank Burke promised to build a $10 million downton
park near the Tennessee Aquarium if fans would agree to buy at
least 1,800 season tickets and 10 luxury boxes. They did and now
Chattanooga has one of the most beautiful stadiums in the minors.
(Curtright, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).25. WITH PHOTOS.
