   BOX-ALI-TORCH _ ATLANTA _ Nearly four years after the Atlanta
Olympics, the most enduring memory is Ali lighting the torch. A
behind-the-scenes look on how it came about and why it remains such
a cherished moment. (Tierney, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 35.
