   The Boston Globe plans to move to NYTimes News Service
subscribers a special package of stories about the seizure this
morning of 6-year-old Cuban refugee Elian Gonzalez in Miami.
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR; For questions about stories, please contact  &UR; Frank Perrotta
 &LR; at the Boston Globe,  &UR; 617-929-2597. &LR;
