<SLUG> BC-BBN-GIANTS-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A WINNING BALLPARK, BUT A LOSING TEAM
</HEADLINE>
 (With BBO-NOTEBOOK) 
By MURRAY CHASS   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
