this small, working-class burg on the southern outskirts of
Cleveland. Motorcycle cop Rick Hovan has a sharp eye for motorists
who dare to gab on their mobile phones. Brooklyn was the first
municipality in the nation to ban the use of cellular telephones
while driving. (Holmes, Cox News Service). WITH PHOTOS.
