</P>
<P>
   OLDWEST-WOMEN _ Women in the West rarely lived up to the
stereotypes in fiction and film. But they did have tough roles to
fulfill in holding down the homestead while men conquered trails
and herded cattle. (Pierson, Austin American-Statesman). MOVED
</P>
