Showtime started its decline in 1988. Magic may be gone, but
Shaquille O'Neal is now providing the power and Kobe Bryant the
finesse for the Lakers as they head towards a possible championship
this year. O'Neal during a game against the New Jersey Nets earlier
this season. (G. Paul Burnett/The New York Times)
