NYT-04-22-00 1946EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT20000422.0223 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-22 19:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4510 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w BC-ELIAN-RIOTS-0423-1STL     04-22 1886
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIAN-RIOTS-0423-1STLD-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    EDs: updates, tightens throughout . . .
 &HT;    MIAMI ERUPTS FOLLOWING FEDERAL GOVERNMENT SEIZURE OF ELIAN
 &HT;    (1200&AMP;ADD)
