<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIAN-REUNION-0423-1STLD-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    EDs: updates with Miami family attempting to see Elian, Juan
Miguel . . .
 &HT;    ELIAN, JUAN MIGUEL REUNITED AT ANDREWS AFB
 &HT;    With CUBA-ELIAN-0423.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (w) Washington categories.
